betterquesting:10.desc:8: Look around in the crates for a way to open the door!
After you enter the main station area, you might be able to piece together a suit with a small amount of oxygen left.
Once you've found the §aCrowbar§r by looting various storages, use it on some of the blocks making up your walkway and the crates around.

You find yourself on a ship, lost in space.


Enter one of these commands to begin:

§6/station create§r - If playing by yourself or starting a team.
§6§a/station invite [player]§r - The invite command asks another player to join your island.
§a§2/station join§r - The join command will have you join an island if recently asked by the invite command.
Split your Iron into nuggets and cook them again for Wrought Iron.
With these, you'll be able to complete the Recycler and start making more complex materials!
If you look around the ship, you'll be able to find some tools to help you get started.
Craft up a Copper or Iron Furnace for your basic Smelting Needs!
